# Claude agent runtime state (per-machine, never committed)
# — Active Tasks table, Agent Voice persona, local notes
/CLAUDE.local.md

# Codex agent runtime state (per-machine, never committed)
/AGENTS.local.md

# Claude agent run directories (local only — contents never committed)
# Alternate path conventions in field repos: `run/CLAUDE-RUNS/` (singular),
# `runs/` (flat, no subdir), `temp/CLAUDE-RUNS/` (POC). Adjust if applicable.
runs/
!runs/.gitkeep
!runs/CLAUDE-RUNS/.gitkeep
!runs/CLAUDE-RUNS/ARCHIVE.template.md

# Note: ARCHIVE.md and any ARCHIVE-YYYY-MM.md files stay ignored (per-dev archive history).
# Only ARCHIVE.template.md is tracked — see archive-run skill Step 4.5 for monthly rotation.

# Log files
*.log
